-- Standard Chartered Hires Shah From Deutsche Bank for Middle East M&A Team
-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 2010-10-19T06:54:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/standard-chartered-hires-shah-from-deutsche-bank-to-head-m-a-in-mideast.html
Standard Chartered Plc appointed
Apoorva Shah as managing director of mergers and acquisitions
for the Middle East and North Africa region.  Shah, who will be based in Dubai, joins the bank from
Deutsche Bank AG, where he was the regional head of mergers and
acquisitions, Standard Chartered said in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  